des: SeeSaw is your ultimate fashion destination. We carry a carefully curated collection of pieces from the world’s top fashion designers, often selected directly off the runways of Milan and Paris for each season’s latest looks. Founded in 2004 by CEO, stylist, and fashion influencer Gina Curko, the company has expanded to two store locations in Tenafly and Fort Lee, NJ. As a luxury lifestyle brand intended to dress the sexy, sophisticated woman from head to toe, SeeSaw lifts up the modern woman to be her best and most beautiful self.
